    title: 'Category',
    options: SNIPPET_CATEGORIES.map(c => ({
      label: c.label,
      value: c.value,
    })),
  },
];
```

**Search criteria:**
- Name match: `e.name.toLowerCase().includes(lower)`
- Keyword match: `e.keyword.toLowerCase().includes(lower)`
- Content match: `e.content.toLowerCase().includes(lower)`
- Category filter: `e.category === filterValue`

---

### Summary Table

| Component | File | Query Match Methods | Filter Type | Key Line Numbers |
|-----------|------|---------------------|------------|------------------|
| **App.tsx (Root)** | `/src/App.tsx` | title, subtitle, keywords, aliases | Commands/Applications | 290-380, 332-336 |
| **Clipboard** | `/src/components/clipboard_history/clipboard_history_view.tsx` | content, sourceApp | Content Type | 203-221 |
| **Emoji Picker** | `/src/components/emoji_picker/emoji_picker_view.tsx` | name, keywords, char | Category | 130-148 |
| **File Search** | `/src/components/file_search/file_search_view.tsx` | name, path | File Type | 154-172 |
| **Snippet Manager** | `/src/components/snippet_manager/snippet_manager_view.tsx` | name, keyword, content | Category | 356-375 |
| **Command Registry** | `/src/registry/command_registry.ts` | title, subtitle, keywords, aliases | None (used by root) | 58-85 |

All search implementations use the pattern: **convert to lowercase and use `.includes()`** for case-insensitive substring matching.

